WEBVTT

00:00:30.520 --> 00:00:33.856
because "feels like dying"
is not scientific enough.

00:00:33.880 --> 00:00:34.896
(Laughter)

00:00:34.920 --> 00:00:36.120
I checked.

00:00:37.080 --> 00:00:38.376
During my transition,

00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:40.353
my husband was pressing down on my sacrum

00:00:40.377 --> 00:00:41.816
to keep my body from breaking.

00:00:41.840 --> 00:00:45.040
My father was waiting
behind the hospital curtain ...

00:00:46.040 --> 00:00:47.280
more like hiding.

00:00:48.240 --> 00:00:50.040
But my mother was at my side.

00:00:51.560 --> 00:00:55.056
The midwife said
she could see the baby's head,

00:00:55.080 --> 00:00:58.456
but all I could feel was a ring of fire.

00:00:58.480 --> 00:01:00.536
I turned to my mother and said, "I can't,"